{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":751,"text":"This summer I was back\nin Ohio for a family wedding,"},{"time":7784,"text":"and when I was there,"},{"time":9985,"text":"there was a meet and greet\nwith Anna and Elsa from \"Frozen.\""},{"time":13478,"text":"Not the Anna and Elsa from \"Frozen,\""},{"time":17103,"text":"as this was not a Disney-sanctioned event."},{"time":19833,"text":"These two entrepreneurs had\na business of running princess parties."},{"time":24433,"text":"Your kid is turning five?"},{"time":26017,"text":"They'll come sing some songs,\nsprinkle some fairy dust, it's great."},{"time":29554,"text":"And they were not about\nto miss out on the opportunity"},{"time":33168,"text":"that was the phenomenon\nand that was \"Frozen.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":35804,"text":"So they get hired by a local toy store,"},{"time":37701,"text":"kids come in on a Saturday morning,"},{"time":39458,"text":"buy some Disney swag, get their\npicture taken with the princesses,"},{"time":42557,"text":"call it a day."},{"time":44160,"text":"It's like Santa Claus\nwithout the seasonal restrictions."},{"time":46857,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":48463,"text":"And my three-and-a-half-year-old niece\nSamantha was in the thick of it."},{"time":53550,"text":"She could care less that these two women\nwere signing posters and coloring books"},{"time":58672,"text":"as Snow Queen and Princess Ana\nwith one N to avoid copyright lawsuits."},{"time":63956,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":65123,"text":"According to my niece and the 200-plus\nkids in the parking lot that day,"},{"time":69819,"text":"this was the Anna and Elsa from \"Frozen.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":75955,"text":"It is a blazing hot Saturday morning\nin August in Ohio."},{"time":81598,"text":"We get there at 10 o'clock,\nthe scheduled start time,"},{"time":84873,"text":"and we are handed number 59."},{"time":87106,"text":"By 11 o'clock they had called\nnumbers 21 through 25;"},{"time":91674,"text":"this was going to be a while,"},{"time":93427,"text":"and there is no amount\nof free face painting or temporary tattoos"},{"time":97892,"text":"that could prevent the meltdowns\nthat were occurring outside of the store."},{"time":101397,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":102972,"text":"So, by 12:30 we get called:"},{"time":107114,"text":"\"56 to 63, please.\""},{"time":110316,"text":"And as we walk in, it is a scene\nI can only describe you"},{"time":113678,"text":"as saying it looked like Norway threw up."},{"time":116568,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":117948,"text":"There were cardboard\ncut-out snowflakes covering the floor,"},{"time":122334,"text":"glitter on every flat surface,\nand icicles all over the walls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":127870,"text":"And as we stood in line"},{"time":129063,"text":"in an attempt to give\nmy niece a better vantage point"},{"time":131596,"text":"than the backside\nof the mother of number 58,"},{"time":134151,"text":"I put her up on my shoulders,"},{"time":135880,"text":"and she was instantly riveted\nby the sight of the princesses."},{"time":139979,"text":"And as we moved forward,\nher excitement only grew,"},{"time":142520,"text":"and as we finally got\nto the front of the line,"},{"time":144804,"text":"and number 58 unfurled her poster\nto be signed by the princesses,"},{"time":148498,"text":"I could literally feel the excitement\nrunning through her body."},{"time":152098,"text":"And let's be honest,\nat that point, I was pretty excited too."},{"time":155063,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":156458,"text":"I mean, the Scandinavian decadence\nwas mesmerizing."},{"time":159457,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":160626,"text":"So we get to the front of the line,"},{"time":162536,"text":"and the haggard clerk\nturns to my niece and says,"},{"time":165546,"text":"\"Hi, honey. You're next!"},{"time":167366,"text":"Do you want to get down,\nor you're going to stay"},{"time":169656,"text":"on your dad's shoulders for the picture?'"},{"time":171913,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":173400,"text":"And I was, for a lack\nof a better word, frozen."},{"time":177262,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":178874,"text":"It's amazing that in an unexpected instant\nwe are faced with the question,"},{"time":183667,"text":"who am I?"},{"time":184998,"text":"Am I an aunt? Or am I an advocate?"},{"time":188466,"text":"Millions of people have seen my video\nabout how to have a hard conversation,"},{"time":192297,"text":"and there one was, right in front of me."},{"time":194614,"text":"At the same time,"},{"time":195686,"text":"there's nothing more important\nto me than the kids in my life,"},{"time":198596,"text":"so I found myself in a situation\nthat we so often find ourselves in,"},{"time":202544,"text":"torn between two things,\ntwo impossible choices."},{"time":205767,"text":"Would I be an advocate?"},{"time":207794,"text":"Would I take my niece off my shoulders\nand turn to the clerk and explain to her"},{"time":212342,"text":"that I was in fact\nher aunt, not her father,"},{"time":215480,"text":"and that she should be more careful"},{"time":217849,"text":"and not to jump to gender conclusions\nbased on haircuts and shoulder rides --"},{"time":222605,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":223741,"text":"and while doing that,"},{"time":225598,"text":"miss out on what was, to this point,\nthe greatest moment of my niece's life."},{"time":231116,"text":"Or would I be an aunt?"},{"time":233206,"text":"Would I brush off that comment,\ntake a million pictures,"},{"time":236344,"text":"and not be distracted for an instant\nfrom the pure joy of that moment,"},{"time":241322,"text":"and by doing that,"},{"time":242841,"text":"walk out with the shame that comes up\nfor not standing up for myself,"},{"time":246224,"text":"especially in front of my niece."}]},{"cues":[{"time":248607,"text":"Who was I?"},{"time":250410,"text":"Which one was more important?\nWhich role was more worth it?"},{"time":255230,"text":"Was I an aunt? Or was I an advocate?"},{"time":258219,"text":"And I had a split second to decide."}]},{"cues":[{"time":262235,"text":"We are taught right now"},{"time":263814,"text":"that we are living in a world\nof constant and increasing polarity."},{"time":268113,"text":"It's so black and white,\nso us and them, so right and wrong."},{"time":273524,"text":"There is no middle,\nthere is no gray, just polarity."},{"time":277691,"text":"Polarity is a state in which\ntwo ideas or opinions"},{"time":280132,"text":"are completely opposite from each other;"},{"time":282712,"text":"a diametrical opposition."},{"time":286127,"text":"Which side are you on?"},{"time":288581,"text":"Are you unequivocally and without question\nantiwar, pro-choice, anti-death penalty,"},{"time":292646,"text":"pro-gun regulation, proponent\nof open borders and pro-union?"},{"time":296104,"text":"Or, are you absolutely \nand uncompromisingly"},{"time":301337,"text":"pro-war, pro-life, pro-death penalty,\n"},{"time":303522,"text":"a believer that the Second\nAmendment is absolute,"},{"time":305838,"text":"anti-immigrant and pro-business?"},{"time":307542,"text":"It's all or none, you're with us\nor against us."},{"time":309787,"text":"That is polarity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":312247,"text":"The problem with polarity \nand absolutes is that"},{"time":317191,"text":"it eliminates the individuality\nof our human experience"},{"time":322355,"text":"and that makes it contradictory\nto our human nature."},{"time":327187,"text":"But if we are pulled\nin these two directions,"},{"time":329297,"text":"but it's not really where we exist --"},{"time":331077,"text":"polarity is not our actual reality --"},{"time":333507,"text":"where do we go from there?"},{"time":334887,"text":"What's at the other end of that spectrum?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":338368,"text":"I don't think it's an unattainable,\nharmonious utopia,"},{"time":342408,"text":"I think the opposite\nof polarity is duality."},{"time":345842,"text":"Duality is a state of having two parts,"},{"time":348446,"text":"but not in diametrical opposition,"},{"time":351730,"text":"in simultaneous existence."},{"time":354676,"text":"Don't think it's possible?"},{"time":356663,"text":"Here are the people I know:"},{"time":358334,"text":"I know Catholics who are pro-choice,\nand feminists who wear hijabs,"},{"time":361497,"text":"and veterans who are antiwar,"},{"time":363202,"text":"and NRA members who think\nI should be able to get married."},{"time":365987,"text":"Those are the people I know,\nthose are my friends and family,"},{"time":369023,"text":"that is the majority of our society,\nthat is you, that is me."},{"time":372000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":380717,"text":"Duality is the ability\nto hold both things."},{"time":385886,"text":"But the question is:\nCan we own our duality?"},{"time":390008,"text":"Can we have the courage\nto hold both things?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":394230,"text":"I work at a restaurant in town,"},{"time":396422,"text":"I became really good friends\nwith the busser."},{"time":399032,"text":"I was a server and we had \na great relationship,"},{"time":402050,"text":"we had a really great time together."},{"time":403990,"text":"Her Spanish was great"},{"time":407609,"text":"because she was from Mexico."},{"time":409451,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":411313,"text":"That line actually went the other way."},{"time":413747,"text":"Her English was limited,\nbut significantly better than my Spanish."},{"time":419848,"text":"But we were united by our similarities,"},{"time":423678,"text":"not separated by our differences."},{"time":426578,"text":"And we were close, even though\nwe came from very different worlds."},{"time":429698,"text":"She was from Mexico,\n"},{"time":430838,"text":"she left her family behind\nso she could come here"},{"time":434169,"text":"and afford them a better life back home."},{"time":436166,"text":"She was a devout conservative Catholic,"},{"time":439106,"text":"a believer in traditional family values,"},{"time":441826,"text":"stereotypical roles of men and women,"},{"time":443933,"text":"and I was, well, me."},{"time":446728,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":448633,"text":"But the things that bonded us\nwere when she asked about my girlfriend,"},{"time":452319,"text":"or she shared pictures that she had\nfrom her family back home."},{"time":455788,"text":"Those were the things\nthat brought us together."},{"time":458416,"text":"So one day, we were in the back,"},{"time":460003,"text":"scarfing down food as quickly as we could,\ngathered around a small table,"},{"time":463683,"text":"during a very rare lull,"},{"time":465313,"text":"and a new guy\nfrom the kitchen came over --"},{"time":467323,"text":"who happened to be her cousin --"},{"time":468985,"text":"and sat down with all\nthe bravado and machismo"},{"time":471788,"text":"that his 20-year-old body could hold."},{"time":473950,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":475772,"text":"And he said to her,\n[in Spanish] \"Does Ash have a boyfriend?\""},{"time":481904,"text":"And she said,\n[in Spanish] \"No, she has a girlfriend.\""},{"time":487386,"text":"And he said,\n[in Spanish] \"A girlfriend?!?\""},{"time":490912,"text":"And she set down her fork,\nand locked eyes with him,"},{"time":494025,"text":"and said, [in Spanish] \"Yes,\na girlfriend. That is all.\""},{"time":499048,"text":"And his smug smile quickly dropped\nto one of maternal respect,"},{"time":503941,"text":"grabbed his plate, walked off,\nwent back to work."},{"time":507144,"text":"She never made eye contact with me."},{"time":509668,"text":"She left, did the same thing --"},{"time":511384,"text":"it was a 10-second conversation,\nsuch a short interaction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":514655,"text":"And on paper, she had\nso much more in common with him:"},{"time":517191,"text":"language, culture, history, family,\nher community was her lifeline here,"},{"time":522289,"text":"but her moral compass trumped all of that."},{"time":526461,"text":"And a little bit later, they were joking\naround in the kitchen in Spanish,"},{"time":530124,"text":"that had nothing to do with me,"},{"time":532025,"text":"and that is duality."},{"time":534470,"text":"She didn't have to choose some P.C. stance\non gayness over her heritage."},{"time":538983,"text":"She didn't have to choose\nher family over our friendship."},{"time":542134,"text":"It wasn't Jesus or Ash."},{"time":544409,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":548556,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":555183,"text":"Her individual morality\nwas so strongly rooted"},{"time":559761,"text":"that she had the courage\nto hold both things."},{"time":563143,"text":"Our moral integrity is our responsibility"},{"time":566325,"text":"and we must be prepared to defend it\neven when it's not convenient."},{"time":570557,"text":"That's what it means to be an ally,\nand if you're going to be an ally,"},{"time":573870,"text":"you have to be an active ally:"},{"time":576158,"text":"Ask questions, act when you hear\nsomething inappropriate,"},{"time":580046,"text":"actually engage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":582075,"text":"I had a family friend who for years\nused to call my girlfriend my lover."},{"time":588531,"text":"Really? Lover?"},{"time":590976,"text":"So overly sexual,"},{"time":593001,"text":"so '70s gay porn."},{"time":595047,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":599293,"text":"But she was trying, and she asked."},{"time":601789,"text":"She could have called her my friend,"},{"time":603573,"text":"or my \"friend,\" or my \"special friend\" --"},{"time":607708,"text":"(Laughter) --"},{"time":609093,"text":"or even worse, just not asked at all."},{"time":612059,"text":"Believe me, we would rather have you ask."},{"time":615690,"text":"I would rather have her say lover,\nthan say nothing at all."}]},{"cues":[{"time":620932,"text":"People often say to me,\n\"Well, Ash, I don't care."},{"time":623964,"text":"I don't see race\nor religion or sexuality."},{"time":627757,"text":"It doesn't matter to me. I don't see it.\""},{"time":631910,"text":"But I think the opposite of homophobia\nand racism and xenophobia is not love,"},{"time":637245,"text":"it's apathy."},{"time":638859,"text":"If you don't see my gayness,\nthen you don't see me."},{"time":642963,"text":"If it doesn't matter to you\nwho I sleep with,"},{"time":645949,"text":"then you cannot imagine what it feels like"},{"time":648135,"text":"when I walk down the street\nlate at night holding her hand,"},{"time":651011,"text":"and approach a group of people\nand have to make the decision"},{"time":653829,"text":"if I should hang on to it\nor if I should I drop it"},{"time":656175,"text":"when all I want to do\nis squeeze it tighter."},{"time":658494,"text":"And the small victory I feel"},{"time":661012,"text":"when I make it by\nand don't have to let go."},{"time":663720,"text":"And the incredible cowardice\nand disappointment I feel when I drop it."},{"time":668839,"text":"If you do not see that struggle"},{"time":670788,"text":"that is unique to my human experience\nbecause I am gay, then you don't see me."},{"time":677264,"text":"If you are going to be an ally,\nI need you to see me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":682679,"text":"As individuals, as allies, as humans,\n"},{"time":685622,"text":"we need to be able to hold both things:"},{"time":688622,"text":"both the good and the bad,\n"},{"time":691070,"text":"the easy and the hard."},{"time":692900,"text":"You don't learn how to hold\ntwo things just from the fluff,"},{"time":697372,"text":"you learn it from the grit."},{"time":699774,"text":"And what if duality\nis just the first step?"},{"time":704308,"text":"What if through compassion\nand empathy and human interaction"},{"time":709138,"text":"we are able to learn to hold two things?"},{"time":711533,"text":"And if we can hold\ntwo things, we can hold four,"},{"time":713848,"text":"and if we can hold four,\nwe can hold eight,"},{"time":715859,"text":"and if we can hold eight,\nwe can hold hundreds."}]},{"cues":[{"time":718100,"text":"We are complex individuals,\n"},{"time":720562,"text":"swirls of contradiction."},{"time":722362,"text":"You are all holding\nso many things right now."},{"time":725888,"text":"What can you do to hold just a few more?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":730100,"text":"So, back to Toledo, Ohio."},{"time":732237,"text":"I'm at the front of the line,"},{"time":734417,"text":"niece on my shoulders,\nthe frazzled clerk calls me Dad."},{"time":738520,"text":"Have you ever been mistaken\nfor the wrong gender?"},{"time":743111,"text":"Not even that."},{"time":745310,"text":"Have you ever been called\nsomething you are not?"},{"time":751509,"text":"Here's what it feels like for me:"},{"time":754040,"text":"I am instantly an internal storm\nof contrasting emotions."},{"time":758114,"text":"I break out into a sweat that is\na combination of rage and humiliation,"},{"time":763657,"text":"I feel like the entire store\nis staring at me,"},{"time":766618,"text":"and I simultaneously feel invisible."},{"time":769179,"text":"I want to explode in a tirade of fury,"},{"time":772123,"text":"and I want to crawl under a rock."},{"time":774717,"text":"And top all of that off\nwith the frustration that I'm wearing"},{"time":777820,"text":"an out-of-character\ntight-fitting purple t-shirt,"},{"time":781418,"text":"so this whole store can see my boobs,"},{"time":783456,"text":"to make sure this exact\nsame thing doesn't happen."},{"time":786458,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":788640,"text":"But, despite my best efforts\nto be seen as the gender I am,"},{"time":792962,"text":"it still happens."},{"time":794804,"text":"And I hope with every ounce\nof my body that no one heard --"},{"time":799497,"text":"not my sister, not my girlfriend,\nand certainly not my niece."},{"time":804050,"text":"I am accustomed to this familiar hurt,"},{"time":806491,"text":"but I will do whatever I need to do\nto protect the people I love from it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":811906,"text":"But then I take my niece off my shoulders,"},{"time":814441,"text":"and she runs to Elsa and Anna --"},{"time":816616,"text":"the thing she's been\nwaiting so long for --"},{"time":819183,"text":"and all that stuff goes away.\n"},{"time":821270,"text":"All that matters is the smile on her face."},{"time":824980,"text":"And as the 30 seconds we waited\ntwo and a half hours for comes to a close"},{"time":830638,"text":"we gather up our things,\nand I lock eyes with the clerk again;"},{"time":835842,"text":"and she gives me\nan apologetic smile and mouths,"},{"time":838979,"text":"\"I am so sorry!\""},{"time":841276,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":843386,"text":"And her humanity, her willingness to admit\nher mistake disarms me immediately,"},{"time":849243,"text":"then I give her a: \"It's okay,\nit happens. But thanks.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":854416,"text":"And I realize in that moment"},{"time":857407,"text":"that I don't have to be"},{"time":859445,"text":"either an aunt\nor an advocate, I can be both."},{"time":864903,"text":"I can live in duality,\nand I can hold two things."},{"time":870252,"text":"And if I can hold two things\nin that environment,"},{"time":873190,"text":"I can hold so many more things."},{"time":875543,"text":"As my girlfriend and my niece hold hands\nand skip out the front of the door,"},{"time":879296,"text":"I turn to my sister and say,\n\"Was it worth it?\""},{"time":882040,"text":"And she said, \"Are you kidding me?"},{"time":883815,"text":"Did you see the look on her face?\nThis was the greatest day of her life!\""},{"time":887703,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":888801,"text":"\"It was worth the two\nand a half hours in the heat,"},{"time":891759,"text":"it was worth the overpriced coloring book\nthat we already had a copy of.\""},{"time":896147,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":897855,"text":"\"It was even worth you \ngetting called Dad.\""},{"time":901510,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":905205,"text":"And for the first time ever\nin my life, it actually was."}]},{"cues":[{"time":910920,"text":"Thank you, Boulder. Have a good night."}]},{"cues":[{"time":913099,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}